"Shear Stiffness — Timoshenko Beam
'Constant shear deformation (Logan Ch.4)

"Shear deformation
#deq γ = dw/dx - θ

"B Matrix
#sym diff(1-t; t)
#sym diff(t; t)

"Stiffness Matrix
#deq K_shear = G*A_s/L*[1; -1 | -1; 1]

"Numerical
G = 80000MPa
A_s = 40cm^2
L = 3m
K_s = G*A_s/L*[1; -1 | -1; 1]
K_s|[kN/m; kN/m | kN/m; kN/m]
